        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[Xcode에 Swift Formatter 적용하기]]></title>
            <link>https://kukuluku.github.io/xcode-swift-formatter</link>
            <guid>https://kukuluku.github.io/xcode-swift-formatter</guid>
            <pubDate>Sat, 11 Jan 2025 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[Xcode16에서 Swift 코드를 작성 중 자동으로 동작하는(Format On Save) formatter를 적용해 보았다.]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Xcode16에서 Swift 코드를 작성 중 자동으로 동작하는(Format On Save) formatter를 적용해 보았다.</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="swiftformat-설치">SwiftFormat 설치<a href="https://kukuluku.github.io/xcode-swift-formatter#swiftformat-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to SwiftFormat 설치" title="Direct link to SwiftFormat 설치">​</a></h2>
<p>homebrew를 통해 설치 후 Xcode의 익스텐션으로 사용할 수 있도록 구성해 보았다.</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://github.com/nicklockwood/SwiftFormat" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">github</a></li>
</ul>
<ol>
<li>homebrew를 통해 swiftformat-for-xcode 설치</li>
</ol>
<div class="codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-text codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">brew install --cask swiftformat-for-xcode</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
<ol start="2">
<li>설치 된 swiftformat-for-xcode 를 실행한다.</li>
</ol>
<img width="487" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/8ba3fb10-53a7-4b32-be82-34c7f3474709">
<ol start="3">
<li>설정 &gt; 일반 &gt; 로그인 항목 및 확장 프로그램 &gt; SwiftFormat for Xcode 체크</li>
</ol>
<img width="705" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/e5cceaab-7a7d-4fbd-8d41-763dffc58ca4">
<ol start="4">
<li>Xcode에서 저장 시 SwiftFormat &gt; Format File 을 동작하도록 Key Binding 을 수정한다.<br>
<!-- -->Xcode &gt; Settings &gt; Key Bindings
<img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/c91a8511-b6a9-4748-8bc7-ef658a3fa377" alt="image" class="img_ev3q"></li>
</ol>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="결론">결론<a href="https://kukuluku.github.io/xcode-swift-formatter#%EA%B2%B0%EB%A1%A0" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to 결론" title="Direct link to 결론">​</a></h2>
<p>이렇게 저장 시 자동으로 Swift formatting을 하도록 적용해 보았다. 추가로 프로젝트에 .swiftformat 파일을 추가하면 해당 프로젝트에 swift convention 설정이 가능하다.</p>]]></content:encoded>
